title: Ep. - 180 - AMANDA STANTON FROM THE BACHELOR - TYLER WHITMAN FROM MILLION DOLLAR LISTING NEW YORK
description:
Amanda Stanton from The Bachelor and Bachelor in Paradise talks about dating after the show, what it is really like to stay at the Bachelor in Paradise resort, and her thoughts on two of her exes being involved in the Chrisley family drama. 


Tyler Whitman from Million Dollar Listing New York talks about being cast for the show, working in the rigorous New York real estate market, and his inspiring weight loss journey. 


My son Jack reviews Hard Knocks on HBO. 


Reality Life with Kate Casey
